“For our fathers, for us, for our children and for our descendants—Your word is good and 
lasting—a Law that will never be abrogated.”—Kuzari\par
{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*82>}82{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}The word help indicates that the recipient also participated in his rescue, whereas the 
