{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*14>}14{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}The word {\highlight7 @hh}{\highlight7 <HEB>}\rtlch \'e5\'cc\'e1\'c0\'eb\'c5\'ef{\highlight7 {\ltrch @ee}}{\highlight7 {\ltrch<}{\ltrch ENG}{\ltrch>}}\ltrch , ‘and so,’ marks the beginning of the special prayers of the Shemoneh Esreh 
