{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*19>}19{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}The nations of the world will finally prostrate themselves before You, i.e. submit to You 
