{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*28>}28{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Even as Hashem Himself is forever true, and even as His word, the Torah and the promise 
