{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*12>}12{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}According to Targum Yonassan, Hashem had compassion on Yishmael, and heard his 
