{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*13>}13{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}As Hashem was about to spare Yishmael, certain angels argued that he did not deserve 
