{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*28>}28{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Devarim 33:5. Rashi says that Hashem was King of Yisrael only when the tribes of Yisrael 
