{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*31>}31{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}The words {\highlight7 @hh}{\highlight7 <HEB>}\rtlch \'e5\'cc\'f9\'d2\'c0\'e0\'e5\'cc \'f4\'cc\'c4\'fa\'c0\'e7\'c5\'e9 \'f2\'e5\zwj\'c9\'ec\'c8\'ed{\highlight7 {\ltrch @ee}}{\highlight7 {\ltrch<}{\ltrch ENG}{\ltrch>}}\ltrch , “and lift up entranceways to eternity,” imply that the gates of the 
