{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*76>}76{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}This is based on Yechezkel 18:32, ‘For I do not desire the death of him that dies, but rather 
