{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*38>}38{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Justice is one of the three pillars upon which the earth rests ( Maseches Avos 1:18). Without 
