{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*39>}39{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}Psalm 94, “Mighty one of retribution” was sung on the fourth day because Hashem created 
