{\highlight7 @b1}{\highlight7 <EM>}{\highlight7 <EN>}{\highlight7 <*41>}41{\highlight7 @b2}{\highlight7 <EN>}On the sixth day, the Levites sang psalm 93, “Adonoy is King, He has clothed Himself in 
